                                    <h2><strong>WHAT DO WE USE YOUR PERSONAL DATA FOR?</strong></h2>
                                    <p>All personal data submitted on our website will be used for processing the visa by Kenyan eVisa Service Team only. Be assured that we will not disclose personal Information to third parties without your permission. Once the service is completed, the eVisa sent to the applicant, all the private information and record will be transferred to our customer storing profile. Kenyan eVisa Service Team uses e-mail to notify you of the changes in the status of your visa applications, changes in the database or our website, new services, features or promotions. Special notes: Only under special circumstances, request for an individual approval letter should be sent to our email address: <strong><a href="mailto:support@thekenyanvisa.com" target="_top">support@thekenyanvisa.com</a></strong></p>
